input_data.subject: Freight Quote Request - Q2025-004 - Construction Co
input_data.body:
Dear Sarah Johnson,

We would like to request a freight quote for Construction Co.

Quote Details:
- Quote Number: Q2025-004
- Project Description: Building materials and installation services
- Contact Person: Mike Brown
- Date: 2025-11-25

Please provide pricing for:
- Freight transportation
- Loading/unloading services
- Insurance coverage
- Delivery timeline

Thank you for your consideration.

Best regards,
Mike Brown

Mike Brown
Sales Representative
Lane County Project Management
